title: Kid Nichols N173 Old Judge Cabinet

posts.post_title: Kid Nichols N173 Old Judge Cabinet
posts.post_content:
POP 1! Only N173 Nichols ever to be graded by SGC (or PSA for that matter)

In fact, I don't think I've seen one of these publicly offered for sale in all my years collecting. I figured I'd take it out and see if anyone is interested. 

$60k shipped and insured.
